MooX::Attributes::Shadow

NAME

    MooX::Attributes::Shadow - shadow attributes of contained objects

DESCRIPTION

    This module provides utility functions (and a role) to 
    easy for a container class to shadow contained classes'
    attributes.


DEPENDENCIES

    Moo
    Moo::Role
    MooX::Types::MooseLike

INSTALLATION


    To compile, test and install:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


CHANGES

    See the Changes file for more details

